#######################

### Supply to Ionic Pool
POST {{baseUrl}}/beta/v0/ionic/supply/optimism
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sender": "0x1234567890123456789012345678901234567890",
  "call_data": {
    "asset": "WETH",
    "amount": 1.5,
    "on_behalf_of": "0x1234567890123456789012345678901234567890"
  }
}

